data.value: The 2016 Ford Fusion represents a blend of style, performance, and comfort in the midsize sedan segment. Equipped with a range of engine options, the Fusion offers versatility to suit various driving preferences. The base model features a 2.5-liter 4-cylinder engine, delivering a respectable balance of power and efficiency. Paired with a smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission, it provides ample acceleration and achieves competitive fuel economy. Its sleek exterior design, characterized by a bold front grille and available 18-inch alloy wheels, exudes confidence on the road. Inside, the Fusion offers a spacious and well-appointed cabin with supportive seating and a user-friendly infotainment system. Advanced safety features such as traction control and antilock brakes ensure stability and confidence in various driving conditions. With a mileage of 40,000 miles and a price of $12,000, the 2016 Ford Fusion presents an attractive option for drivers seeking a reliable and stylish sedan without compromising on performance or comfort.
